page.title: 11WALROW OTHERS
page.content: ON THIS INDUSTRIAL ESTATE,A LARGE NUMBER OF SMALL ENTERPRISES HAVE BECOME ESTABLISHED AND ARE GROWING. FIVE TRANSPORT UNITS NOW EXSIST.EACH BEGAN WITH ONE MAN AND ONE VEHICLE.ONE NOW SPECIALISES IN THE TRANSPORT OF GRAIN AND HAS INCREASED ITS VEHICLES TO TEN AND ITS STORAGE AREA.ANOTHER HAS LOW LOADERS AND HAS TRANSPORTED A NUMBER OF OLD STEAM ENGINES. THE MILK MAKETING BOARD HAS TWENTY SIX VEHICLES WHICH COLLECT MILK FROM FAMS OVER A VERY WIDE AREA. APART FROM TRANSPORT,THERE IS A VARIETY OF EMPLOYERS,RANGING FROM SPECIALISTS IN THE PROVISION,AND ERECTION OF SHELVING,TO THE MAKING OF FANS AND BLOWERS,TO THE PROVISION OF HEAVE PLANT FOR ROAD BUILDING AND SITE WORK.
